PrecisRe-appointment of Marilyn Hébert, of Ste-Sophie, Quebec, as a full-time temporary member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office) to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years, effective September 1, 1990.
